Package: worldfoundry-engine-build-deps
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: World Foundry <packages@worldfoundry.org>
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: build-essential,
 cmake (>= 3.22),
 libx11-dev,
 libgl1-mesa-dev,
 libglu1-mesa-dev,
 gdb,
 xxd,
 python3,
 pkg-config,
 git,
 curl,
 wget,
 unzip
Homepage: https://worldfoundry.org/
Description: build dependencies for the World Foundry engine
 Pulls in everything required to compile the World Foundry C++17 engine
 (build_game.sh) and its vendored libraries (Jolt, miniaudio, zForth,
 Lua, QuickJS, etc.). All deps are vendored in-tree; this metapackage
 covers only the system-side toolchain and headers.
 .
 This is the lowest-common-denominator package — install
 worldfoundry-dev if you also want the asset compilers, Blender addon,
 and retro-porting tools.
